{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father even spoke to a German farmer who-- who lived next to where we had our holiday house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he liked to come and conversate with him, because he spoke German, and that way he could just remember his school days, when he was learning German.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there weren't many Jewish community in Western Poznan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were more in the east of Poznan, but I wasn't aware of any at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had not heard of any anti-semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, I-- I read something in the paper once.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the-- through the German propaganda, which they tried to instill hatred in our country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Something about the Jewish community being-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to buy various things for various reasons, and cheating the farmers, and so on-- which, in effect, I didn't realize, because I wasn't old enough to understand all this.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't aware then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was more aware near the outbreak of war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the German propaganda used to shout that they want the passage through the corridor, Danzig, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I realized, when the Polish army was mobilized and so on, that something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, I heard nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents were very, very upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And naturally, my father wanted to join the Polish army, as well, if necessary to fight for the country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was at that time, when the war broke out, a bit-- before the war broke out, just a few days, we moved-- I, my twin brother, moved to Warsaw in order to join the Polish forces.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the war was that quick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the first day of the war, we were returning from our holiday house to Poznan.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
